          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I know I've said it over and over on the blog already, but I had the best Thanksgiving week. This is more like a full week re-cap because Thanksgiving break started for us last Tuesday night. We drove out to Harpers Ferry that evening after work to meet my parents and brother. Immediately, the games began! The favorite game of the week was Ticket to Ride."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
