          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " My sisters were supposed to arrive Wednesday evening, but the weather prevented my dad from being able to leave Harpers Ferry to get them from the airport."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "On Thanksgiving Day, my mom and I put the rest of the meal together while Daniel, Dad, and my brother went to pick up my sisters from our apartment in Northern Virigina. When we were all together, we took a cheesy sibling + in-law picture on the cabin's fancy spiral staircase!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
