              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Thanksgiving evening was spent watching movies with my mom and sisters."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Friday we packed up and drove into Northern Virginia. We had one last meal all together, and then my parents and brother went to the airport for their flight home. My sisters got to stay one more day, so we filled the rest of Friday night and Saturday with some great meals out, The Theory of Everything (fantastic movie by the way), and lots of Gilmore Girls at home."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Saturday evening Daniel and I went to Barnes & Noble (our office) to get some work done. We took the picture below to say goodbye to this B&N location since it was probably our last time to go there - we move to Texas in two weeks!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
