          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Sunday morning we went to church and out to lunch at a local Mexican place. We ended the evening with A Christmas Carol at Ford's Theater. This is a show I have wanted to seeÂ each Christmas we have been here, so we made it happen this year. It was such a great production, and it really got us into the Christmas spirit!"
          }
